{% comment %}
  brand-root.liquid — v1.1 (BRAND-APPROVED)
  Single source of truth for Libertas Loqui principle voice.
  Use: {% render 'brand-root' %} on every template.
  Human override: Forest only. No Foxify. No third-party classes.
{% endcomment %}

<div class="brand-root page-width">
  <div class="brand-principle text-center">
    <p class="principle-statement text-balance">
      The right to speak openly is the foundation of clear thinking and American liberty.
    </p>
    <p class="mission text-balance">
      Libertas Loqui exists so every independent thinker, entrepreneur, and veteran can wear the principle without fear—calmly, confidently, and with intellectual courage.
    </p>
    <p class="mission text-balance">
      We make apparel that reminds the wearer: ideas improve when they are tested in open dialogue.<br>
      No slogans that divide. Only the quiet declaration that freedom of speech belongs to everyone who values truth over comfort.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="trust-bar flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-2 text-sm text-muted border-t border-border pt-6 mt-8">
    <span class="trust-item">🇺🇸 First Amendment Protected</span>
    <span class="trust-item">USA-made on premium Bayside blanks</span>
    <span class="trust-item">Free replacement on defects</span>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .brand-root {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .principle-statement {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: rgb(var(--color-foreground));
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .mission {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: #4b5563;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .trust-bar {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #6b7280;
  }
  .trust-item {
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
</style>
